 Gospel singer, Judikay and her husband Anselem Opara are now proud parents. The couple have welcomed their first child, a baby boy together. Judikay announced on her Instagram page that she delivered a bouncing baby boy on Tuesday, March 22, 2022. Sharing a photo of her baby’s hand as she held it, the ‘More Than Gold’ hitmaker expressed her heartfelt gratitude to God for this amazing gift. See screenshot below;  Similarly, Nigerian actor Mustapha Sholagbade and his wife welcomed a baby boy in the United Kingdom, yesterday. The tall, dark-skinned actor took to social media to announce the good news, thanking God for another opportunity given to his family. Read more